'''Roğer Federer''' d-amyurar n waddal n Tennis tmurt n [[teswist|Taswist]] ilul ass n {{azmez|8|ɣuct|1981}} di temdint n [[Bâle]].
Seg usegwas n 1998 ig vda yetturar d tervaɛt tameqṛant, iḥarz amḍiq amenzu n ubellez n ATP azal n 237 imalas yemseḍfaren (285 ḥalarmi d 6 Yunyu 2010). Ass n 8 Yulyu 2012, yebwi tadwilt n Wimbledon i tikelt tis sa, yeqḍad amyurar Pete Sampras deg umḍan n tedwilin n Wimbledon ig ḥrez aked imalas ig ella di tqacucut n ubellez n ATP (Imalas wis 286).

Iḥrez ar assa 75 Izwilen, garasen 23 imeqṛanen (17 n Grand Chelems d 6 teqvucin n Masters) d 20 n Masters 1000. Yebwi kuz n izwilen n Grand Chelem ig ellan, win n [[Lusṭrali]], win n lpari di [[Fṛansa]], win n Wimbledon di tmurt n [[Lengliz]], win Flushing meadows di [[Marikan|Timura Yedduklen n Marikan]].

Deg ubellez n Sports Illustrated n usegwas 2010, Roğer Federer d-anadal wis sin yettxelliṣen aṭas n yedrimen deffir [[Tiger Woods]] imi yeṣṣaweḍ ar assa azal n 72 Ifeḍ n dullar deg izwilen yark ig urar.
